  m_Text: "The special day has come once again.\n\nFroggy arrives at the towering
    spire to meet someone important, only to discover that the stairs have collapsed
    after years of neglect.\n\nFortunately, Froggy is a frog. Determined to reach
    the top, he decides to make his way up the tower the only way he knows how\u2014by
    jumping."
